[I] Library supporting dataclasses, datetimes, and numpy

[T] orjson is a fast, correct JSON library for Python. It benchmarks as the
[T] fastest Python library for JSON and is more correct than the standard json
[T] library or other third-party libraries. It serializes dataclass, datetime,
[T] numpy, and UUID instances natively.

